      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "the tobacco GAPdH (cytosolic glyceraldehyde-3-phosphate dehydrogenase) gene (Accession number: M14419, [CITATION_1] ) and the relative transcript values then calculated."
